Package com.irurueta.navigation.frames

Class CoordinateTransformationMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.frames.CoordinateTransformationMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class CoordinateTransformationMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Contains a coordinate transformation matrix, or rotation matrix. The coordinate transformation matrix is a 3x3 matrix where a vector may be transformed in one step from one set of resolving axes to another by pre-multiplying it by the appropriate coordinate transformation matrix. The coordinate transformation matrix is associated to a source and destination frame.
